SUMMARY:Toddler Music and Movement with ILS
DESCRIPTION:New 6-Week Music & Movement Session starts today! \nOur Toddler Music and Movement class is more than singing and dancing—it’s an interactive music class where children learn to feel music in their bodies. Over six weeks\, we’ll explore percussion\, echoing and sequencing\, counting and marching\, ear training\, and early piano sounds. Some classes will feature percussion instruments\, while others include guitar or ukulele\, and drums. \nWith their caregivers\, children will learn to find the beat\, move their feet\, and build early music foundations through joyful routine and repetition. Regular attendance is encouraged so kids can settle into the rhythm and grow with confidence. \nA wonderful first step into music learning for young children. \nLearn more and register here.
URL:https://myballard.com/event/toddler-music-and-movement-with-ils/
LOCATION:Illumination Learning Studio – Greenwood\, 7720 Greenwood Ave N\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/Music-and-Movement-Rev-10.2-3-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Illumination Learning Studio":MAILTO:info@ilskids.com
END:VEVENT
