SUMMARY:The Swapanistas Present: Swap! A Women's Clothing Exchange
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready to swap up your style? \nThen join us for Swap 2026! \nSwap is an amazing event where you let go of your gently used clothing and accessories and trade them in for items that make you feel brand new\, while having fun and supporting a good cause: proceeds and clothing donations benefit local organizations for underserved women and kids. \nWe are excited to announce that this year’s event is being hosted in partnership with the Phinney Neighborhood Association\, truly making this a community event! \n​​Come check it out\, and bring your friends! \nSwap: Saturday March 14th\, 10 AM – 1:30 PM\nItem Drop-off: Friday March 13th\, 5 PM – 8 PM \nFor tickets and more info\, please visit our website: https://www.swapanistas.org/ \nPlease email us with questions: swapanistas@gmail.com \nHope to see you there!
URL:https://myballard.com/event/the-swapanistas-present-swap-a-womens-clothing-exchange/
LOCATION:Phinney Neighborhood Center\, 6532 Phinney Ave N Room 7\, Seattle\, 98103\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/Swap-Closet.jpeg
END:VEVENT
