SUMMARY:Oscars Watch Party
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate the 2026 Academy Awards!\nUrban Family Brewing and Film & Froth present the 2026 Oscars Watch Party hosted at the Urban Family Taproom in Ballard. Come grab a seat and watch the show while enjoying some wonderful Seattle beer and great company!\nPrizes to be raffled off include Urban Family Brewing gift cards\, merch\, and Film & Froth merch. \nDon’t forget to enter the Film & Froth Oscars Contest (https://www.filmfroth.com/oscars) to compete for more prizes! \nKids and well behaved dogs on leashes are welcome downstairs in the taproom. The loft is 21+ and no animals are allowed. Check out Urban Family’s website for more information on their taproom! \nWe hope to see you there to celebrate another amazing year of film with fantastic beer and the great people of Urban Family Brewing!
URL:https://myballard.com/event/oscars-watch-party/
LOCATION:Urban Family Brewing\, 1103 NW 52nd St\, Seattle\, WA 98107\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/OscarsWatchParty2026Pic-scaled.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Film &amp%3B Froth":MAILTO:admin@filmfroth.com
END:VEVENT
