SUMMARY:Impossible Loves Romance Improv Show at Swoon City
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to a Impossible Loves\, a romance made up on the spot from your suggestions. Laugh\, care\, and swoon with your friend or foe as Impossible Loves improvises a brand new romance just for you! \nDiscover Impossible Loves\, a team of improvisers creating new worlds and new romances from your suggestions. Each one-hour improvised play opens by asking the audience about times they fell in love. From those moments\, Impossible Loves will create a brand-new romance show. Enjoy a world where anyone and anything can find a happy ending. \nThis show will take place at Swoon City.
