SUMMARY:Gem Painting: Dazzling Book Covers Class at Swoon City
DESCRIPTION:In this delightful 2 hour workshop\, you’ll learn how place gem rhinestones on the cover of your favorite book to create a dazzling design sure to be the star of your shelfie. \nOne note – you will likely NOT COMPLETE a book cover in two hours but you will be able to do the lettering or other design elements. However you will take home up to gems and other supplies to finish your project at home\, if you choose. \nYou can choose a book in the store which is valued $20 or less\, or you can bring your own book\, and receive at $15 store credit. \nAfter the workshop\, you’ll have all the skills you’ll need to continue your gem painting journey. No experience necessary\, beginners welcome. \nThis class will take place at Swoon City.
URL:https://myballard.com/event/gem-painting-dazzling-book-covers-class-at-swoon-city/
LOCATION:Swoon City\, 1716 NW Market St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/bedazzle.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Swoon City":MAILTO:info@swoon.city
END:VEVENT
