SUMMARY:IMPROV SHOW: Impossible Loves
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to a Impossible Loves\, a romance made up on the spot from your suggestions. Laugh\, care\, and swoon with your friend or foe as Impossible Loves improvises a brand new romance just for you! \nDiscover Impossible Loves\, a team of improvisers creating new worlds and new romances from your suggestions. Each one-hour improvised play opens by asking the audience about times they fell in love. From those moments\, Impossible Loves will create a brand-new romance show. Enjoy a world where anyone and anything can find a happy ending.
URL:https://myballard.com/event/improv-show-impossible-loves/
LOCATION:Swoon City\, 1716 NW Market St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2026-01-09-at-4.49.47-PM.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Swoon City":MAILTO:info@swoon.city
END:VEVENT
