SUMMARY:Polymer Clay Earrings Class
DESCRIPTION:“Thanks\, I made them myself!” \nThis will be you responding to the many compliments you will get on the fun\, colorful and one of a kind earrings you will make in this workshop! Join WonderSpace Workshops for an afternoon of creativity and community and learn all of the basics of working with polymer clay. This approachable and beginner-friendly medium is very adaptable and lends itself well to so many different styles from funky\, colorful and bold to classic\, sophisticated and polished. You will leave the workshop with several pairs of completed earrings and armed with new skills to continue the crafting journey at home!
URL:https://myballard.com/event/polymer-clay-earrings-class/
LOCATION:Swoon City\, 1716 NW Market St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/earring.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Swoon City":MAILTO:info@swoon.city
END:VEVENT
