SUMMARY:Painting Class: Watercolor Landscapes for Beginners
DESCRIPTION:This step-by-step\, instructor-led watercolor class is designed for beginners who want to learn how to paint beautiful landscapes with confidence. No prior experience is needed. \nYou’ll be guided through the essential techniques used in watercolor landscape painting\, including: \nBasic and graded washes\nComposition fundamentals\nLayering to create depth and atmosphere\nColor mixing for natural\, harmonious tones \nWith hands-on practice and individual guidance\, you will learn how to build a painting from start to finish and create your own completed landscape by the end of the session. \nThe class is held in a relaxed and supportive environment\, making it a comfortable and encouraging space for total beginners. \nAll materials and supplies are provided\, including a take-home watercolor kit (valued at $20) so you can continue practicing beyond the classroom. \nThis class will take place at Swoon City.
URL:https://myballard.com/event/painting-class-watercolor-landscapes-for-beginners/
LOCATION:Swoon City\, 1716 NW Market St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/watercolor.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Swoon City":MAILTO:info@swoon.city
END:VEVENT
