SUMMARY:Glass Class: Book Cover Coasters
DESCRIPTION:Cozy-up with a mug of tea and your favorite book… but oh no! Where are all the coasters? Have no fear! We’ve got just the solution to protect your precious objects from destructive heat and moisture — glass book coasters. That’s right! Coasters designed by you to look just like your favorite book cover or classic novels\, so that you can enjoy your next book with some extra special\, on-theme decor. \nIn this 3-hour glass charm workshop\, you will build unique compositions using Elmer’s glue and a variety of glass dots\, stringers\, shapes\, and more. Learn the fundamentals of fusing while experimenting with a new medium and exploring the many possibilities! Cost includes all tools and supplies as well as materials for up to 2 coasters per person. Finished pieces will be ready for pick-up at the workshop location after 1 week.
URL:https://myballard.com/event/glass-class-book-cover-coasters/
LOCATION:Swoon City\, 1716 NW Market St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98107\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://myballard.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2026-02-10-at-9.52.32-PM.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Swoon City":MAILTO:info@swoon.city
END:VEVENT
